&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Internship Dates&lt;/strong&gt; –&lt;strong&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;January 24 through May 26, 2028&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Orientation Week&lt;/strong&gt; –&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt; January 24 through January 28, 2028&lt;/p&gt;
